## Notes

The role of an intelligence engine is not to create educational understanding.

Its role is to prepare educational knowledge for the next stage of the Understanding Pipeline.

Every engine answers a different educational question.

Observation Engine

> What happened?

Pattern Engine

> What keeps recurring?

Evidence Engine

> Why should this pattern be trusted?

Confidence Framework

> How confident are we?

Insight Engine

> What might this mean?

Only after these questions have been answered progressively can trustworthy educational understanding emerge.

---

## Final Principle

> **Educational understanding is not generated by a single engine.**

> **It emerges through a progressive sequence of specialized knowledge transformations.**

Every engine prepares.

The pipeline understands.